Overview
This project is a simple web-based stopwatch application that allows users to start, stop, pause, resume, and reset a timer. It also features lap time recording and supports multiple themes with customizable display sizes, button colors, and sounds.

Features
Start, Stop, Pause, Resume: Control the stopwatch with these buttons.
Lap Recording: Record lap times during the stopwatch operation.
Display Milliseconds: View milliseconds along with hours, minutes, and seconds.
Theme Support: Toggle between light and dark themes.
Sound Effects: Play sounds for button clicks, lap records, and resets.
Responsive Design: Ensures a good user experience on various devices.